The paper is about improving the performance of a learning to rank algorithm for document retrieval in search engines. This topic falls under information retrieval (cs.IR) and machine learning (cs.LG) categories. The paper also discusses the use of decision trees, which is a common technique in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and natural language processing (cs.CL). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of features, which is relevant to computer vision (cs.CV) as well.
